                                "description": "<p>It is well known that &lsquo;prevention is better than cure&rsquo; and this package is designed specifically for that purpose. It includes a unique diagnostic profile of tests for a comprehensive health evaluation at an early age. It screens the most common health conditions related to heart, diabetes, urine and blood. You should get this package done on an annual basis if you are above 30 years of age and want a thorough evaluation of the overall health status of your body.</p>",
