request.description:
Description:

- Creates a new subscription request where the user allows an HIU to access their health

- Defines categories, HIU ID, patient ID, consent period, and purpose.


Notes

- This is the **start of the subscription workflow**.

- The backend generates a subscription request (which the user may accept automatically depending on the flow).

- Requires the same header set as API 1.


Body:

``` json
{
    "subscription": {
        "categories": [
            "LINK",
            "DATA"
        ],
        "hiu": {
            "id": "IN3610001058"
        },
        "patient": {
            "id": "{{abhaAddress}}"
        },
        "period": {
            "from": "2025-12-13T08:02:17.960Z",
            "to": "2125-12-25T08:01:17.960Z"
