request.description:
Description:

- This endpoint modifies an existing locker subscription, allowing updates to access details or linked ABHA information.

- Primarily used when a user needs to update their locker link or refresh subscription metadata.


Notes:

- Requires the full authorization header pack (`sessionId`, `Authorization`, `X-CM-ID`, and `abhaAddress`).

- Used to adjust or refresh subscription details without creating a new one.


Body:

``` json
{
    "hiuId": "{{hiuId}}",
    "subscriptionEditAndApprovalRequest": {
        "isApplicableForAllHIPs": true,
        "includedSources": [
            {   
                "hiTypes": [
                    "DiagnosticReport",
                    "Prescription",
                    "ImmunizationRecord",
                    "DischargeSummary",
                    "OPConsultation",
                    "HealthDocumentRecord",
                    "WellnessRecord"
                ],
                "purpose": {
                    "text": "Care Management",
                    "code": "CAREMGT",
                    "refUri": "www.abdm.gov.in"
                },
                "categories": [
